Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:09.42,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}（勉強宣告安全○）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:11.20,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}△關係的麻煩
