Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.39,0:22:48.01,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}好想試試啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.33,0:22:50.09,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}因為這是戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:54.62,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}比天空更寬廣  比海洋更深沉
